ActJUDGES ACT (RESIDENCE FOR TRAVEL ALLOWANCE PURPOSES)
PrecisOrder prescribing an additional period during which certain RELOCATION EXPENSES may be reimbursed to the Hon. KEITH D. YAMAUCHI, who was required to relocate to the City of Edmonton in Alberta following his appointment as a Judge of the Court of Queen’s Bench of Alberta on December 13, 2007.
